            <title>[CASSANDRA-14579] Set broadcast address in internode messagaing handshake</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-14579</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
